OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloudy with hill fog across the
OL,6,FPennines, patchy light rain easing but
OL,7,Fshowers developing later. Elsewhere
OL,8,Fmainly dry and cloudy, some bright
OL,9,Fspells developing. Feeling warm and
OL,10,Fhumid. Breezy.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FRemaining cloudy with rain
OL,13,Flikely in the west and over high
OL,14,Fground, more settled and drier in the
OL,15,Feast. Winds easing slightly but breezy
OL,16,Falong the coast.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
