OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CSunday:FCloudy and breezy for much of
OL,6,Fthe period with spells of rain at
OL,7,Ftimes, mostly affecting western hills
OL,8,Fwith drier conditions further east.
OL,9,FTemperatures gradually creeping up and
OL,10,Fbecoming warm.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FMonday
OL,13,Fand Tuesday, cloudy with spells of
OL,14,Frain at times, mostly affecting
OL,15,Fwestern hills with drier conditions
OL,16,Ffurther east. Wednesday becoming drier
OL,17,Fand sunnier. Temperatures becoming
OL,18,Frather warm.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
